### Patient mit Geburtsnamen (use=maiden + humanname-own-name Extension)
# @name patient-geburtsname
# Expected: OperationOutcome with "all ok" (no errors)
# AK1: Geburtsname via use=maiden und humanname-own-name Extension (de.basisprofil.r4)
POST http://localhost:8080/fhir/Patient/$validate?profile=https://fhir.cognovis.de/praxis/StructureDefinition/fpde-patient
Authorization: Basic basic:secret
Content-Type: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "Patient",
  "name": [
    {
      "use": "official",
      "family": "Mueller",
      "given": ["Anna"]
    },
    {
      "use": "maiden",
      "family": "Schmidt",
      "_family": {
        "extension": [{
          "url": "http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/humanname-own-name",
          "valueString": "Schmidt"
        }]
      }
    }
  ],
  "birthDate": "1985-04-22"
}

###

### Patient ohne Geburtsnamen (muss weiterhin valide sein)
# @name patient-ohne-geburtsname
# Expected: OperationOutcome with "all ok" (no errors)
# AK1: Geburtsname ist optional — Patient ohne maiden name muss valide bleiben
POST http://localhost:8080/fhir/Patient/$validate?profile=https://fhir.cognovis.de/praxis/StructureDefinition/fpde-patient
Authorization: Basic basic:secret
Content-Type: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "Patient",
  "name": [{
    "use": "official",
    "family": "Bauer",
    "given": ["Thomas"]
  }],
  "birthDate": "1970-11-05"
}

###

### Patient mit Ortsteil/Stadtteil in Adresse (iso21090-ADXP-precinct auf Address.extension)
# @name patient-ortsteil
# Expected: OperationOutcome with "all ok" (no errors)
# AK2: Ortsteil via iso21090-ADXP-precinct Extension auf Address.extension (nicht Address.line.extension!)
POST http://localhost:8080/fhir/Patient/$validate?profile=https://fhir.cognovis.de/praxis/StructureDefinition/fpde-patient
Authorization: Basic basic:secret
Content-Type: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "Patient",
  "name": [{
    "use": "official",
    "family": "Gonzalez",
    "given": ["Maria"]
  }],
  "birthDate": "1992-08-14",
  "address": [{
    "line": ["Oranienstrasse 42"],
    "city": "Berlin",
    "postalCode": "10999",
    "country": "DE",
    "extension": [{
      "url": "http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/iso21090-ADXP-precinct",
      "valueString": "Kreuzberg"
    }]
  }]
}

###

### Patient mit Geburtsname UND Ortsteil (kombiniertes Szenario)
# @name patient-geburtsname-und-ortsteil
# Expected: OperationOutcome with "all ok" (no errors)
# AK1 + AK2 kombiniert
POST http://localhost:8080/fhir/Patient/$validate?profile=https://fhir.cognovis.de/praxis/StructureDefinition/fpde-patient
Authorization: Basic basic:secret
Content-Type: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "Patient",
  "name": [
    {
      "use": "official",
      "family": "Weber",
      "given": ["Sabine"]
    },
    {
      "use": "maiden",
      "family": "Klein",
      "_family": {
        "extension": [{
          "url": "http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/humanname-own-name",
          "valueString": "Klein"
        }]
      }
    }
  ],
  "birthDate": "1978-03-15",
  "address": [{
    "line": ["Schwanenstrasse 7"],
    "city": "Hamburg",
    "postalCode": "20249",
    "country": "DE",
    "extension": [{
      "url": "http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/iso21090-ADXP-precinct",
      "valueString": "Eppendorf"
    }]
  }]
}


### Validate FPDEPatient — Invalid: birthDate in falschem Format (FHIR date-Typ verletzt)
# @name validate-patient-invalid-birthdate
# Expected: OperationOutcome mit Fehler
# FHIR-Datentyp date erfordert das Format YYYY, YYYY-MM oder YYYY-MM-DD.
# "1990-13-45" hat Monat 13 und Tag 45 — ungültig, muss Fehler liefern.
POST http://localhost:8080/fhir/Patient/$validate?profile=https://fhir.cognovis.de/praxis/StructureDefinition/fpde-patient
Authorization: Basic basic:secret
Content-Type: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "Patient",
  "name": [{
    "use": "official",
    "family": "Testperson",
    "given": ["Invalid"]
  }],
  "birthDate": "1990-13-45"
}

?? status == 200
?? body.issue[0].severity == "error"
